Package albums

Class Album

  • java.lang.Object
    • albums.Album
  • public class Album
extends java.lang.Object
    This class defines the Album abstract data type with title, artist, genre, releaseDate, and isAvailable.
    Author:
    William Wang, Joshua Sze
